    "description": "We at Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Sales Manager based out of Faridabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies:\nJones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jones Lang LaSalle Digital Technologies!",
